title: Crypto VC C1 With Coinbase Lineage Eyes Acquisition in Austalia: Report
description: Crypto venture capital firm C1, which is led by former Coinbase executives, has met with several cryptocurrency groups and Australian venture firms offering to buy private holdings from investors using its $500 million ($AUD 760 million) fund, according to the Australian Financial Review.
